---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Nav from '../components/Nav.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About — Mycelium">
  <Nav />

  <section class="hero-about">
    <div class="container">
      <h1>About Mycelium</h1>
      <p class="subtitle">Documenting indigenous permaculture knowledge before it disappears.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="story">
    <div class="container story-grid">
      <div class="story-text">
        <h2>The Story</h2>
        <p>In August 2025, I took my Permaculture Design Certificate course in Nueva Ecija, hosted by Sir Bert of PPA. That experience changed everything.</p>
        <p>I met Sir Hubert Posadas — an elder Filipino farmer from the Baganihan Collective who had been practicing indigenous composting and farming techniques passed down from his grandfather. Knowledge that was never written down. Knowledge that existed only in his memory.</p>
        <p>I realized: if we don't document this, it dies with the people who hold it.</p>
        <p>I was 16. I knew tech. I could build a bridge between the knowledge holders and the people who need it. That's how Mycelium was born.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="story-image">
        <img src="https://mycelium-learn.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/founder-photo.jpg" alt="Tax Riego" loading="lazy">
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="why-name">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Why "Mycelium"?</h2>
      <p>In nature, mycelium is the underground fungal network that connects trees in a forest. It shares water, nutrients, and chemical signals between plants — even across species. Scientists call it the "Wood Wide Web."</p>
      <p>We do the same thing, but for knowledge. We connect practitioners, researchers, farmers, and learners — sharing what works, what's been forgotten, and what needs to be preserved.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="partners-section">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Our Partners</h2>
      <div class="partners-grid">
        <div class="partner-card">
          <h3>Baganihan Collective</h3>
          <p>Our primary content partner. Led by Sir Hubert Posadas with 6+ pilot sites across the Philippines documenting indigenous permaculture practices.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="partner-card">
          <h3>Philippine Permaculture Association</h3>
          <p>20+ years of permaculture experience in the Philippines. National credibility and an established practitioner network.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="partner-card">
          <h3>Permaculture Research PH</h3>
          <p>Academic research and data collection on permaculture practitioners nationwide. Mapping the permaculture landscape of the Philippines.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="cta-about">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Join the Network</h2>
      <p>Whether you're a farmer, a student, a researcher, or simply curious — Mycelium is for you. Free, always.</p>
      <a href="/resources" class="cta-button">Explore Resources</a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <footer class="footer">
    <div class="container footer-inner">
      <div class="footer-brand">
        <span class="logo-text">MYCELIUM</span>
        <p>Free permaculture education for the Philippines.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="footer-links">
        <a href="/about">About</a>
        <a href="/videos">Videos</a>
        <a href="/resources">Resources</a>
        <a href="/events">Events</a>
      </div>
      <div class="footer-social">
        <a href="https://instagram.com/mycelium.learn" target="_blank">Instagram</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </footer>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .hero-about {
    background: var(--olive);
    padding: 100px 0 60px;
    text-align: center;
  }
  .hero-about h1 {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: 3rem;
    color: var(--cream);
    font-weight: 400;
    font-style: italic;
  }
  .subtitle {
    color: rgba(245,237,212,0.7);
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    margin-top: 16px;
  }
  .story {
    background: var(--cream);
    padding: 80px 0;
  }
  .story-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1.2fr 0.8fr;
    gap: 60px;
    align-items: center;
  }
  .story-text h2 {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    color: var(--text-dark);
  }
  .story-text p {
    font-size: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.75;
    color: #444;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }
  .story-image img {
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 350px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    margin: 0 auto;
    display: block;
  }
  .why-name {
    background: var(--olive);
    padding: 80px 0;
    text-align: center;
  }
  .why-name h2 {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: 2rem;
    color: var(--cream);
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }
  .why-name p {
    color: rgba(245,237,212,0.8);
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    max-width: 700px;
    margin: 0 auto 16px;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }
  .partners-section {
    background: var(--cream);
    padding: 80px 0;
  }
  .partners-section h2 {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: 2rem;
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 48px;
    color: var(--text-dark);
  }
  .partners-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 32px;
  }
  .partner-card {
    padding: 28px;
    background: white;
    border-radius: 12px;
    box-shadow: 0 2px 12px rgba(0,0,0,0.06);
  }
  .partner-card h3 {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
    color: var(--olive);
  }
  .partner-card p {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: #555;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }
  .cta-about {
    background: var(--charcoal);
    padding: 80px 0;
    text-align: center;
  }
  .cta-about h2 {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: 2rem;
    color: var(--cream);
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }
  .cta-about p {
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.6);
    margin-bottom: 28px;
  }
  .cta-button {
    display: inline-block;
    background: var(--gold);
    color: var(--text-dark);
    padding: 14px 36px;
    border-radius: 50px;
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    transition: background 0.2s;
  }
  .cta-button:hover { opacity: 0.9; }
  .footer { background: var(--charcoal); padding: 60px 0; }
  .footer-inner { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: flex-start; gap: 40px; }
  .footer-brand .logo-text { font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 0.12em; color: var(--white); font-size: 1rem; }
  .footer-brand p { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5); font-size: 0.85rem; margin-top: 8px; }
  .footer-links, .footer-social { display: flex; gap: 24px; }
  .footer-links a, .footer-social a { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.6); font-size: 0.85rem; transition: color 0.2s; }
  .footer-links a:hover, .footer-social a:hover { color: var(--white); }
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .hero-about h1 { font-size: 2.2rem; }
    .story-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .partners-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .footer-inner { flex-direction: column; }
  }
</style>
